# Data / logs
*.log
# Anchored to the repo root on purpose: this is for the LongMemEval datasets, which are
# large and externally sourced. Unanchored it would also swallow web/data/, whose two
# generated JSON files ARE the site's content and must be committed.
/data/
*.sqlite

